window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Arthur never knew the comfort of home—until he died. Now, reborn in a vibrant demon world, he's serving up more than just tea; he's crafting the life he always dreamed of, one friendship at a time.</b></p> <p>Arthur didn't plan on being reincarnated into a world full of demons. But after the initial misunderstandings were cleared away, he found himself exactly where he wanted to be: in a world that was nice.</p> <p>It doesn't take long before a community of friendly demons forms around Arthur, helping him find his place in this new world. With each bubble that rises in his tea, Arthur rises too—learning to love, to belong, and to truly live for the first time in two lifetimes.</p> <p>Demon World Boba Shop <i>is more than just a story—let this heartwarming tale be your escape into a cozy fantasy world where everyone belongs and happiness is always on the menu.</i></p> <p><i>The first volume in a delightful LitRPG series, </i>Demon World Boba Shop <i>promises to bring warmth to your heart and a smile to your face. This story features a wholesome narrative, well-crafted plot, likable characters, and overall coziness. In a world that often feels overwhelming, </i>Demon World Boba Shop <i>is a haven: the perfect listen for anyone needing a breather.</i></p> <p><i>Includes a special note from the author.</i> </p><p></p>"; 
